metadata.description: After an age of peace, a new dictator has emerged. The Freedom Apes decide to take matters into their own hands and foil his plans. Your Freedom Ape doubles as your avatar in the political metaverse game, where you can help stop the dictator Puck Footin. 40-75% of the mint price of your Freedom Ape will go to 'Razom for Ukraine', a 501(c) charity. Visit www.FreedomApesClub.com for more details.
metadata.name: Freedom Apes Club
